        {
            "_id": "SUvl7lPOVDiTyjX4",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Rejuvenation",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a hungry ghost is destroyed, they reform after [[/gmr 2d4 #days]]{2d4 days} fully healed at the location where they were last destroyed. They're only permanently destroyed when they have been given a proper burial, have had their grave cleaned and maintained for at least a year, or have been judged to be redeemed by Pharasma.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
